latestIgtvVideos.title: #dontrushchallenge
Makeup look using only 5 products ❤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello there my lovelies, 
I have created a causal date/ everyday wearable look using just 5 makeup products. 
However, I have dome my skin care routine and prepped my canvas in prior.

Don't forget to like, share and follow. 
Products used: -concealer: @maybelline @maybelline.india instant age rewind concealer in CARAMEL - Blush Palette: @makeuprevolution in shade HOT SPICE
-@maybelline @maybelline.india colossal 22 hour kajal in black
-Lipstick: @kikomilano Arctic Holiday collection in 05
-Mascara: @toofaced @toofacedindia better than sex mascara mini 
Hope you like it ❤
